## 🛠️ Useful Verification Commands (Quick Reference)

```bash
show vlan brief                        # List all VLANs
show interfaces trunk                  # Show trunk port status
show ip interface brief               # Show all interfaces + status
show ip route                         # Show routing table
show ip access-lists                  # Show ACLs and hit counts
show ip nat translations              # Show NAT table
show running-config                   # Show full current config
show running-config | section vlan    # Filter config for VLAN section
show cdp neighbors                    # Show connected Cisco devices
ping 10.10.20.10                      # Test connectivity
traceroute 10.10.30.10               # Trace path to destination
```
